{"tid":1432413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府就公務員集會意見上線啦！","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:53:31.000Z","uid":62032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"31fe2b7cdf175fc2306ef4c5bc1418ff51c76d66","tid":1432413,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有關你對公務員隊伍／集會的意見<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n先生/女士：<br />\n<br />\n你的電郵已收悉。<br />\n<br />\n公務員隊伍有不少核心價值和原則：必須奉公守法、堅守法治、盡忠職守、不<br />\n偏不倚、政治中立等。這些信念亦是廣大市民對我們的期望。我們理解有部分同事對<br />\n於近日的事態有他們的想法。公務員事務局已提醒公務員同事表達自己的意見時，應<br />\n確保有關意見不會引致與其本身的職務有利益衝突，或可能令人認為有損其在執行職<br />\n務時不偏不倚和政治中立的重要原則。公務員須時刻確保他們的行為不會妨礙他們以<br />\n專業、公正的態度執行公務。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，勞工處的同事都堅守崗位，努力執行職務，我們深信同事們會繼續<br />\n盡心盡力為市民服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勞工處處長<br />\n（ 羅靜琳 代行）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b234894d06a8cb7f99e42a7a4732944d9ddc28","tid":1432413,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"x is 0 if x &gt;= 0 for all real x"},{"pid":"90c869d4291b2ace6107b1488069cbda739ea074","tid":1432413,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"if x&lt;0, x is unreal"},{"pid":"011f952bb7c23f74981f25b9503dc426bc5eeff0","tid":1432413,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c869d4291b2ace6107b1488069cbda739ea074","tid":1432413,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"if x&lt;0, x is unreal"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}